Packagecom.splunk.services.search
Classpublic class SearchJobResults
InheritanceSearchJobResults flash.events.EventDispatcher

The SearchJobResults class is used to retrieve the transformed events from an existing search job.

refreshIntervalproperty 
refreshInterval:Number  [read-write]

The length of time, in seconds, between automatic reloads of results. If set to zero or less, automatic reloads are disabled.

The default value is 0.

Implementation
    public function get refreshInterval():Number

Loads results from the associated SearchJob instance. If results are already loading, the load operation is closed.

Parameters
